  "code": "---\ntitle: Class Diagram for OBD Platform\n---\nclassDiagram\n  %% Relationtships\n  User --> OBD_Connection : uses\n  OBD_Connection --> Car: gets\n  Car --> Logs: A scan generates\n  Logs ..> OBD_Code: contains\n\n  class User {\n    - INT user_ID\n    - String name\n    - String last_name\n    - String email\n    - String passwd\n\n    + log_in(email, passwd)\n    + sign_out(user_ID)\n    + change_passwd(old, new)\n    + reset_passwd(email)\n    + delete_account()\n    + suspend_account()\n  }\n\n  class Car {\n    - INT car_ID\n    - String VIN\n    - String brand\n    - String model\n    - String year\n\n    + scan()\n    + show_logs()\n    + perform_analytics()\n    + show_analytics()\n  }\n\n  class Logs {\n    - Enum status\n    - INT occurrence_count\n    - Time created_at\n    - Time updated_at\n  }\n\n  class OBD_Code {\n    - String code\n    - String category\n    - String suffix\n\n    + get_code()\n    - validate_code()\n    + get_description()\n  }\n\n  class OBD_Connection {\n    - String protocol\n    - String device_ID\n    - Boolean connected\n\n    + connect() bool\n    + disconnect() bool\n  }\n",
